Class DmcClassInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.dmd.dmc.DmcClassInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<DmcClassInfo>
public class DmcClassInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DmcClassInfo>

The DmcClassInfo class is a helper class that stores a small amount of information derived from a a ClassDefinition. This information is used to assist during object deserialization and may also be used in filtering.
